{"tid":2431924,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"自從返左份冇壓力既藍領工之後 身心都健康左","createTime":"2021-03-04T03:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T04:18:10.000Z","uid":98473,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e10f8b400a84a352c4af8ca51d7a188dd9a3407","tid":2431924,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"睇到隔離post返工返到食降血壓藥<br />\n就諗返起以前 雖然唔係勁到要食藥<br />\n但都係好大壓力 放工又係咁諗工事<br />\n放假都要覆客 覆老細<br />\n成日失眠 好辛苦<br />\n宜家雖然辛苦d 但都已經學識一門手藝 人工都高過之前好多 <br />\n最緊要係收工就可以洗手走人<br />\n再儲多d經驗同錢重可以跳出黎自己開檔(不過又變返有相對既壓力)"},{"pid":"5bcc33e8d5ce3cabc40af5e7b188a448f73567b9","tid":2431924,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"咩手藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b93f89e6cfa30a80e92666daa6e335c9649082","tid":2431924,"uid":98473,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"5bcc33e8d5ce3cabc40af5e7b188a448f73567b9","tid":2431924,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"咩手藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"sorry 唔想自爆"},{"pid":"a0cd36a3cdd7abb4879696c6cf7f06a0e3186a41","tid":2431924,"uid":26898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:02:46.000Z","msg":"樓主幾多歲轉藍領？<br />\n本身就快40，都有考慮過轉唔轉...<br />\n不過從頭再嚟過怕會好低人工...."},{"pid":"4eb533803978b9cf46ed36b9c8cf0abe8b78ec41","tid":2431924,"uid":78383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bcc33e8d5ce3cabc40af5e7b188a448f73567b9","tid":2431924,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"咩手藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"